---
title: Harissa-Roasted Carrot and Avocado Salad with Israeli Couscous
description: Spicy harissa dressing pairs deliciously with sweet carrots and golden avocado in this hearty dinner salad. Mixed with Isaraeli couscous and topped with sour cream, this is one dish you won't soon forget!
